class.rdfs:comment:
A [[RealEstateListing]] is a listing that describes one or more real-estate [[Offer]]s (whose [[businessFunction]] is typically to lease out, or to sell).
  The [[RealEstateListing]] type itself represents the overall listing, as manifested in some [[WebPage]].
class.rdfs:label: RealEstateListing

schema:datePosted.rdfs:comment: Publication date of an online listing.
schema:datePosted.rdfs:label: datePosted

schema:leaseLength.rdfs:comment: Length of the lease for some [[Accommodation]], either particular to some [[Offer]] or in some cases intrinsic to the property.
schema:leaseLength.rdfs:label: leaseLength
